sphere size 0.1 - 5 (more space for lower values)
cloud offset x, y, z
culling distance - to remove spheres close to the camera, can go (slider from camera to orbit (position - sphere radius))
outlines - OnSelected, OnAll, Off
outline color - RGB (define), Inverted
background color
filter nearby colors + radius - makes a sphere around the selected colors; only colors within the sphere are shown 